short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Replace the GitHub contributions graph with Conway's Game of Life.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The GitHub contributions graph, a public reminder that you might not be working as hard as you should! Especially if your work is all done in private repositories or other platforms.

Now you can replace all contribution graphs on GitHub with Conway's Game of Life, using your contributions as the seed.
